cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with computer vision and natural language processing techniques to analyze traffic camera images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of natural language processing techniques also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses deep learning methods, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves topic modeling, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
